# TalkIt Project Context

- This project is **TalkIt**.
- Do not refer to this project as WASI.
- If older notes mention WASI, treat them as outdated context and prioritize TalkIt.

## Product Scope (current)

- Android app focused on question-based social gameplay.
- Core loop includes showing questions, swiping/advancing, and tracking used questions.
- The reset action can exist during development but is expected to be removed from production UX later.

## Guidance for Future Work

- Keep architecture scalable and modular from early stages.
- Prioritize maintainability, sync-readiness, and mobile performance.
- Prefer incremental deliveries with clear phases and acceptance criteria.
